title: #92Noon! Wild Shutout/Gleeman from Training Camp/Wes Walz/Matt Birk in Studio
description: The Wild win in a shutout, 4-0, against the Vegas Golden Knights. Touching on the Zucker trade and things to come. Some Vikings talk. PA's 'son,' Aaron Techie Gleeman calls in from Training Camp in Florida. FSN's Wes Walz and former Viking Matt Birk in studio.
